# Venv environnment and python libraries config

## Python librairies

pip install numpy pandas matplotlib bokeh space nltk pycausalimpact pptree

### Spacy

python -m spacy download en

## Jupyterlab plugins

jupyter labextension install @jupyterlab/toc @aquirdturtle/collapsible_headings @krassowski/jupyterlab_go_to_definition 

### LSP

https://github.com/krassowski/jupyterlab-lsp

## Shortcuts changes

Shortcuts :

{
    "shortcuts": [
            {
                "command": "application:activate-next-tab",
            "keys": [
                "Alt J"
            ],
            "selector": "body"
            },
            {
                    "command": "application:activate-previous-tab",
            "keys": [
                "Alt K"
            ],
            "selector": "body"
            }
    ]
}

